### ============================================================
### CHAT — Conversations & Messages
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### All endpoints require a valid JWT access token
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = PASTE_CUSTOMER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@courierToken = PASTE_COURIER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@otherUserToken = PASTE_OTHER_USER_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CREATE OR GET CONVERSATION
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Create Conversation — customer starts conversation with courier
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "other_user_id": 5
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Create Conversation — courier starts with customer (roles swapped)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "other_user_id": 1
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Create Conversation — same role (customer ↔ customer) (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "other_user_id": 2
}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Create Conversation — non-existent user (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "other_user_id": 999999
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Conversation — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "other_user_id": 5
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET USER CONVERSATIONS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get My Conversations — authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Conversations — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET MESSAGES IN CONVERSATION
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Messages — conversation participant
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages?skip=0&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [SUCCESS] Get Messages — second page
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages?skip=50&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Messages — IDOR: non-participant accesses conversation (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Messages — non-existent conversation (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/999999/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Messages — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# SEND MESSAGE IN CONVERSATION (multipart/form-data)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Send Text Message — participant sends a text
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MsgBoundary1

------MsgBoundary1
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Hello! I would like to discuss the order details.
------MsgBoundary1
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message_type"

text
------MsgBoundary1--

###

### [SUCCESS] Send Invoice Message — courier creates an invoice in chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MsgBoundary2

------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

هنا تفاصيل الفاتورة
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message_type"

invoice
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="invoice_description"

Birthday cake - chocolate, 2kg
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="invoice_gift_price"

8000
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="invoice_service_fee"

2000
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="invoice_delivery_fee"

1500
------MsgBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="invoice_total"

11500
------MsgBoundary2--

###

### [FAIL — Security] Send Message — non-participant sends message (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MsgBoundary3

------MsgBoundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Unauthorized message attempt
------MsgBoundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message_type"

text
------MsgBoundary3--

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Send Message — invalid message_type (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MsgBoundary4

------MsgBoundary4
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Test message
------MsgBoundary4
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message_type"

invalid_type
------MsgBoundary4--

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Send Invoice Message — missing invoice fields (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MsgBoundary5

------MsgBoundary5
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="content"

Incomplete invoice
------MsgBoundary5
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="message_type"

invoice
------MsgBoundary5--


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET CONVERSATION BY ORDER
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Conversation by Order — participant access
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/by-order/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Conversation by Order — non-participant (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/by-order/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Conversation by Order — no conversation for this order (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/by-order/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# UPDATE CONVERSATION STATUS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Update Conversation Status — mark as inactive
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1?status=inactive
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Update Conversation Status — invalid status value (400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1?status=deleted
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Update Conversation Status — non-participant (403)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/chat/conversations/1?status=inactive
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET MESSAGE MEDIA
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Message Media — participant accesses media message
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages/1/media
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Message Media — non-participant (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages/1/media
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Message Media — message has no media (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/messages/999/media
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET ORDER IMAGE
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Order Image — order creator gets image 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/orders/1/images/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Order Image — non-owner access (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/orders/1/images/1
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Get Order Image — invalid image number (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/chat/orders/1/images/5
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
